The Bifork Pattern

Everything begins with an invariant.

Then it forks into complementary representations.

The purpose of intelligence is to continuously reconcile them.

           Invariant
               │
           (Bifork)
          /         \
 Representation A   Representation B
          \         /
        Feedback & Reconciliation
               │
         Better Invariant

